# Cursor Rules - ArchivistMCP

Rules structure for Cursor AI.

## Files

- **[general.mdc](general.mdc)** — Project rules, tech stack, structure
- **[kotlin.mdc](kotlin.mdc)** — Kotlin conventions, coroutines, null safety
- **[mcp-tools.mdc](mcp-tools.mdc)** — MCP tools, tool definition, resources

## Usage

All rules are automatically loaded by Cursor when working with the project.

## Priorities

1. `general.mdc` — applies to entire project
2. `kotlin.mdc` — for .kt files
3. `mcp-tools.mdc` — for MCP tools